g.text: coBib is a console-based bibliography management tool written in Python. It maintains a plain-text database of literature references in
YAML format and provides various subcommands to work with this database. It also provides an interactive terminal user interface (see also
) to complement its command-line interface (see the [SUBCOMMANDS][] section below).
